    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 MP</strong> to produce 1 of the following effects:</p><p></p><p><strong>Heal:</strong> You gain a pool of healing that you can use to restore HP to any number of creatures within 5 Spaces of you, distributing the HP among them (minimum of 1 HP each). </p><p>Make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check.</strong></p><p><strong>Success:</strong> You can restore up to 3 HP. </p><p><strong>Success (each 5): +1 HP.</strong> </p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> You only restore up to 2 HP.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cure:</strong> You can attempt to remove 1 Poison or Disease from a creature of your choice within 1 Space of you. </p><p>Make a <strong>Spell Check</strong> against the DC of the Poison or Disease. </p><p><strong>Success:</strong> The chosen Poison or Disease ends on the target</p>",
